Package scriptella.driver

Parent package for Scriptella Drivers.

See: Description

Package scriptella.driver Description

Parent package for Scriptella Drivers.

This package is a recommended namespace for various drivers. Scriptella drivers lookup mechanism automatically searches driver classes inside this package without a necessity to specify a full class name. The search procedure is described in DriverFactory class.
